CEO of Multotec Group South Africa, Rikus Immink, shares some of the innovations the company has delivered in the coal sector and highlights why it’s important to have a true local presence and business capability in the South African mining sector. For 45 years, Multotec has helped the world’s biggest mining houses process minerals more efficiently, effectively and reliably. TECH NEWS: Spirals - why they make sense and how they're evolving Backed by recognised industry leaders in metallurgy and process engineering, our mineral processing equipment is used to optimise recoveries and reduce cost of ownership in mineral processing plants in almost 70 countries on six continents.  